              },
              "helpUri": "https://avd.aquasec.com/nvd/cve-2011-3374",
              "help": {
                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2011-3374\nSeverity: LOW\nPackage: libapt-pkg7.0\nFixed Version: \nLink: [CVE-2011-3374](https://avd.aquasec.com/nvd/cve-2011-3374)\nIt was found that apt-key in apt, all versions, do not correctly validate gpg keys with the master keyring, leading to a potential man-in-the-middle attack.",
                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2011-3374**\n| Severity | Package | Fixed Version | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n|LOW|libapt-pkg7.0||[CVE-2011-3374](https://avd.aquasec.com/nvd/cve-2011-3374)|\n\nIt was found that apt-key in apt, all versions, do not correctly validate gpg keys with the master keyring, leading to a potential man-in-the-middle attack."
              },
