              "id": "CVE-2026-42250",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "bzip2: bzip2: Denial of Service in bzip2recover via a specially crafted file"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "bzip2 contains an off‑by‑one error in the bzip2recover utility. When processing a specially crafted file, the application performs an out‑of‑bounds write to a global buffer, resulting in memory corruption and a crash (denial of service).\n\nThis issue was fixed in bzip2 patch 35d122a3df8b0cc4082a4d89fdc6ee99f375fe67"
